        <item>
            <title>1.5.3</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 11:15:20 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>13</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.5.3</h2>
<p>Bills marked paid now stay paid — one-off bills show as Paid instead of counting up overdue days forever, marking a bill paid twice no longer quietly pays next month (and any month that got wrongly marked is repaired), and monthly totals no longer include due dates from before you added the bill.</p>
]]></description>
